  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">An area of <math alttext=\"46.00\"><mn>46.00</mn>\n</math> square nautical miles is equivalent to <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math> square kilometers. To the nearest tenth, what is the value of <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math>? <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 1 nautical mile  equals 1.852 kilometers right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>nautical</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>mile</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>1.852</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>kilometers</mtext></mrow></mfenced></math></p>",
